  "text": "In summary, the importance of the compaction step has been addressed as an essential post-phase in LCS computations. The simplest algorithm was of [CITATION_1] which has a polynomial run-time complexity rather than exponential as in the algorithms of [CITATION_2] and [CITATION_3] .",
